  "fullArabic": "أَيۡنَمَا تَكُونُواْ يُدۡرِككُّمُ ٱلۡمَوۡتُ وَلَوۡ كُنتُمۡ فِي بُرُوجٖ مُّشَيَّدَةٖۗ وَإِن تُصِبۡهُمۡ حَسَنَةٞ يَقُولُواْ هَٰذِهِۦ مِنۡ عِندِ ٱللَّهِۖ وَإِن تُصِبۡهُمۡ سَيِّئَةٞ يَقُولُواْ هَٰذِهِۦ مِنۡ عِندِكَۚ قُلۡ كُلّٞ مِّنۡ عِندِ ٱللَّهِۖ فَمَالِ هَٰٓؤُلَآءِ ٱلۡقَوۡمِ لَا يَكَادُونَ يَفۡقَهُونَ حَدِيثٗا",
  "fullTranslation": "Wherever you may be, death will overtake you, even if you should be within towers of lofty construction. But if good comes to them, they say, \"This is from Allah \"; and if evil befalls them, they say, \"This is from you.\" Say, \"All [things] are from Allah.\" So what is [the matter] with those people that they can hardly understand any statement?",
  "fullTransliteration": "aynama takunu yud'rikkumu al-mawtu walaw kuntum fi burujin mushayyadatin wa-in tusib'hum hasanatun yaqulu hadhihi min indi al-lahi wa-in tusib'hum sayyi-atun yaqulu hadhihi min indika qul kullun min indi al-lahi famali haulai al-qawmi la yakaduna yafqahuna hadithan"
